 da sam krivo rekla

1062
00:48:00,920 --> 00:48:02,600
 milijarde ili milijune

1063
00:48:02,600 --> 00:48:03,440
 ili euro i kune.

1064
00:48:03,440 --> 00:48:04,600
 Znači, takve stvari se dogode.

1065
00:48:04,600 --> 00:48:06,580
 Znači, ako se dogodi greška,

1066
00:48:06,580 --> 00:48:07,440
