 oćete skinuti imunitet,

1087
00:48:27,760 --> 00:48:28,640
 skidam imunitet.

1088
00:48:28,640 --> 00:48:30,080
 Ja sam i otišla iz sabora,

1089
00:48:30,080 --> 00:48:30,840
 nemam imunitet,

1090
00:48:30,840 --> 00:48:31,480
