1091
00:48:31,480 --> 00:48:32,240
 Nije.

1092
00:48:32,240 --> 00:48:33,880
 Čak ni na tim svojim

1093
00:48:33,880 --> 00:48:35,360
 korumpiranim sudovima,

1094
00:48:35,360 --> 00:48:36,440
 i opet ću reći,

1095
00:48:36,440 --> 00:48:37,260
