1102
00:48:43,240 --> 00:48:44,040
 u poreznoj upravi.

1103
00:48:44,040 --> 00:48:45,140
 Niti su svi sudci

1104
00:48:45,140 --> 00:48:45,920
 problem u Hrvatskoj,

1105
00:48:45,960 --> 00:48:47,300
 nego oni koji vode te sudove

1106
00:48:47,300 --> 00:48:48,900
 i oni koji sebe uzimaju pravo

1107
00:48:48,900 --> 00:48:51,420
