 Oleg Butković,

1135
00:49:30,900 --> 00:49:32,360
 Miroslav Šeparović,

1136
00:49:32,360 --> 00:49:33,440
 Plenković,

1137
00:49:33,440 --> 00:49:34,320
 Mesić,

1138
00:49:34,320 --> 00:49:35,720
 Milanović,

1139
00:49:35,720 --> 00:49:36,740
 tako da to nije Hrvatska.

1140
00:49:36,740 --> 00:49:39,160
 To je problem Hrvatske.

1141
00:49:39,160 --> 00:49:41,400
 Hrvatsku ćemo

1142
00:49:41,400 --> 00:49:43,100
 učiniti onakvom

1143
