1247
00:51:51,600 --> 00:51:54,560
 međusobno se obračunavati?

1248
00:51:54,560 --> 00:51:55,320
 To ne znamo.

1249
00:51:55,320 --> 00:51:56,100
 To se može dogoditi

1250
00:51:56,100 --> 00:51:56,800
 preko noći.

1251
00:51:56,800 --> 00:51:58,140
 Znači,

1252
00:51:58,140 --> 00:51:59,960
 ja se ne bavim prognozama

1253
00:51:59,960 --> 00:52:00,620
 kao takvima,

1254
00:52:00,620 --> 00:52:02,080
 ali nastojimo svim

1255
00:52:02,080 --> 00:52:02,920
 i biti spremni

1256
00:52:02,920 --> 00:52:03,740
 u svakom trenutku.

1257
00:52:03,740 --> 00:52:04,320
 Mi danas imamo

1258
00:52:04,320 --> 00:52:06,920
 adekvatnih,

1259
00:52:06,920 --> 00:52:07,600
 adekvatnih,

1260
00:52:07,600 --> 00:52:08,720
 čestitih,

1261
00:52:08,720 --> 00:52:09,180
 moralnih,

1262
00:52:09,180 --> 00:52:09,700
 sposobnih,

1263
