1277
00:52:24,680 --> 00:52:26,140
 Treba se ujediniti.

1278
00:52:26,140 --> 00:52:27,140
 Ko se treba ujediniti?

1279
00:52:27,140 --> 00:52:30,620
 Njihove pulene

1280
00:52:30,620 --> 00:52:31,580
 koje oni stvaraju

1281
00:52:31,580 --> 00:52:32,280
